BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:hdOSQSXuw1EZAxEGBODim
SUMMARY:Improv Greenhouse
DTSTAMP:20260408T030302Z
DTSTART:20260408T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to be surprised\\\, delighted\\\, and maybe even see 
	your wildest idea take on a life of its own!\\n\\n\\n\\nGraduate Greenhous
	e is a Wednesday night showcase featuring alumni from Unexpected Productio
	ns Improv School. Each performance highlights a different alumni group\\\,
	 putting their training to the test with unpredictable scenes\\\, various 
	formats\\\, and improvised stories. From long-form storytelling to charact
	er work\\\, these performers explore the boundaries of improv. \\nJan 7 Ma
	rket Improv \\nJan 14 \\nJan 21 \\nBut the fun doesn’t stop there! Stick a
	round for a double feature as we roll into Seattle’s longest-running Impro
	v Open Mic: the Duos Open Mic! Starting at 8:00 pm\\\, this weekly showcas
	e promises even more laughs\\\, surprises\\\, and improv magic.\n\nhttps:/
	/www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/graduate-greenhouse-fka-an-improvised
	-holiday-special-2-2-2/2026-04-08/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/graduate-greenhouse-fka-an-
	improvised-holiday-special-2-2-2/2026-04-08/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Xuik20uDSrxaytB_VfFhr
SUMMARY:700 Level Student Showcase
DTSTAMP:20260408T030302Z
DTSTART:20260408T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Witness the creation of believable characters\\\, inspiring sce
	nes\\\, and some improv magic by 700 level class.\\n\\n\\n\\nJoin the adva
	nced students in our 700 class and witness them blossom with new improv sk
	ills. Under the guidance of our expert improv teachers\\\, 700 students ar
	e learning new narrative formats and enhancing their skills by working in 
	an ensemble. You get to see the fruits of their efforts by witnessing the 
	creation of believable characters\\\, inspiring scenes\\\, and some improv
	 magic.\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/700-level-student-s
	howcase-2/2026-04-08/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/700-level-student-showcase-
	2/2026-04-08/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:raAFNbAZdfftldzkaOU8S
SUMMARY:Duo Comedy Showcase 2026
DTSTAMP:20260408T030302Z
DTSTART:20260408T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle’s one and only open mic dedicated to two-person improv 
	teams! Every week at Unexpected Productions\\\, two-person teams take the 
	stage to create hilarious\\\, fast-paced\\\, totally unscripted comedy rig
	ht before your eyes. No scripts\\\, no safety nets—just pure improv magic.
	 \\nAt Duos\\\, everyone shines. Newer performers sharpen their game. Seas
	oned improvisers experiment\\\, take risks\\\, and get wonderfully weird. 
	The results? Quick-witted scenes\\\, surprising twists\\\, and bold choice
	s that feel impossible until you watch them happen live. \\nWhether you dr
	eam of being the next Key & Peele\\\, Tina Fey & Amy Poehler\\\, or a chao
	tic tag-team like Deadpool & Wolverine\\\, this is your chance to take the
	 mic and run with it. All experience levels are welcome. Bring a friend\\\
	, form a team\\\, and give Seattle a show they won’t forget. To sign up yo
	ur duo\\\, email duoshowcase@gmail.com. \\nLooking for a midweek serotonin
	 boost? Watching the show is just as fun as performing in it. Grab a seat\
	\\, grab a friend\\\, and discover why Unexpected Productions is the home 
	of Seattle improv.\n\nhttps://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/duo-come
	dy-showcase-2026/2026-04-08/\n\nFrom Unexpected Productions
URL:https://www.unexpectedproductions.org/event/duo-comedy-showcase-2026/20
	26-04-08/
LOCATION:Unexpected Productions\\\, 1428 Post Alley at the Gum Wall in Pike
	 Place Market\\\, Seattle\\\, WA\\\, 98101\\\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:unexpected-productions
CATEGORIES:Unexpected Productions
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
