BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:WFisv2xtTYY6niMaSIc1Y
SUMMARY:No Strings Attached: An Improvised Puppet Show for Grownups
DTSTAMP:20260408T030302Z
DTSTART:20260411T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Seattle’s ORIGINAL improvised puppet show for grownups. An impr
	ovised fever dream with googly eyes and lots of laughter \\n\\n\\n\\n\\nAt
	 Unexpected Productions’ Market Theater\\\, puppets let their hair down (o
	r strings loose) in No Strings Attached—a hilarious\\\, adults improv pupp
	et show. After a long day entertaining the kids\\\, these puppets are read
	y to play—singing bawdy songs\\\, cracking jokes\\\, and getting up to all
	 kinds of outrageous fun. And the best part? You call the shots with your 
	suggestions! \\nDon’t miss this one-of-a-kind comedy show at Pike Place Ma
	rket. It’s puppets\\\, it’s improv\\\, and it’s guaranteed to make you lau
	gh. \\nTHIS SHOW CONTAINS MATURE CONTENT\\\, LANGUAGE\\\, AND SITUATIONS\n
